      "content": "i hear you but i'm just so anxious about the bill. i looked it up online and sometimes facial drooping is just a nerve thing or part of a complex migraine when you're super stressed. if i take some heavy duty magnesium and a sedative to calm down, would that help if it's just a migraine? i really dont want to deal with the hospital if it's just a bad headache.",
